BBVA to Give 350 Employees Early Retirement, Confidencial Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-04-14T05:49:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/bbva-to-give-350-employees-early-retirement-confidencial-says.html
Banco Bilbao Vizcaya Argentaria SA (BBVA) 
is to allow 350 employees to take early retirement as business
in Spain declines,  El Confidencial  said.  The bank will allow employees to retire at 53 years of age,
El Confidencial said, citing unidentified people at BBVA.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at   ablackman@bloomberg.net . 